T1  - International Management Research Meets “The Rest of the World”
AU  - Özkazanç-Pan, Banu
Y1  - 2008/10/01
PY  - 2008
DA  - 2008/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.2008.34422014
DO  - 10.5465/amr.2008.34422014
