T1  - Indeterminacy and the Discourse of Inevitability in International Technology Management
AU  - Leonardi, Paul M.
Y1  - 2008/10/01
PY  - 2008
DA  - 2008/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.2008.34422017
